Ilul '''Ɛumar Drwic''' ɣ 1960 ɣ [[Gulmima]] ɣ iffusugmuḍ n Tmazɣa tutrimt ([[Amṛṛuk]]). Iga yan ɣ imɣnasn n tmsmunt tamttilt tadlsant '''TILILLI''' n Tizi n Yimnayn ([[Gulmima]]); yaru yan Udllis n tmdyazin amsinwal s tmaziɣt d tkatalant ig assaɣ ns: Anfara - Desglaç g usggas n 2005. Iffɣ-d udlis-a g tmazirt n [[Katalunya]].

==Timdyazin==

'''ASERRARU N UZ’MAY'''

:Neggawer s umata,
:Z’min-aɣ ayt ufella,
:Ssgerden-aɣ-d ɣef uya,
:Anelli innqezwa,
:Seg usenti ay negna,
:S tidda d tmira.
:Nekk lliɣ g umaris,
:Afus-inu ig agris,
:Imeddukkal gan aftis,
:Ur amun g Ayt Udlis, 
:Nurzen g ufurrgis.
:Nuwi-d akw isalan
:Seg tmura nn' aɣ-yufan,
:Kerzent digneɣ ifsan
:N umziray d yiman,
:Nɣal is idsent nman,
:Zziɣ tin yigidu d waman.
:Mdin-i-tt amm uslem,
:Iles n yu-nu isusem,
:Tawda digi trekkem,
:Afus da yi-ireggem,
:Tarwa n yiwdan terdem:
:Sgujleɣ-as isem.
:Amekraz ig' i d awullu,
:Z’d’iɣ-as mas ig amlu.
:Dɣi, ukiɣ d ugulu:
:Tewser-nnek ay aseklu,
:Ad teg asfaylu neɣ iflu
:Mek ur tgi gmas i umedlu.

'''SUSS ALUD’ D UGED’RUR!'''

:Tuzlin iswan idammen jjint,
:Allen iz’ran takat md’errant,
:Amaɣus n ustaɣ iga tamtunt,
:Issaley iseggiwar
:G idɣaren ur nbedder.
:Aɣ-am amdaz a tawda
:G taggalt geɣ ad’eggwal!
:Sawlent-i-d tirsal n uslal
:Isennextem wuffal.
:Taselluft n uɣiwel tuzzel,
:Tesferdedda-d taxladda,
:Han ass issudda,
:Id’es n yid’ ibedda.

